::KitKat::

She looked at Megatron. "No Commander. No problem." She looked at 
Timb Bomb and Land Mine. She gave a frustrated sigh.  She would have 
to have a long talk with those two when time permitted. 

The music was starting to blend in her mind and she started humming 
to it without realizing it.
